<p>ing.<br/>The weather now is very good but we have frequent stretches of wet weather probably caused by the heavy bombardments.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;    Our bandmaster now is W. May late bandmaster of Newtown.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;   The 36th are trying to claim us for our old batt'n. but the Colonel here is very reticent about letting us go so we don't know how we will get on.<br/>We have a hut to our selves now &amp; are as happy as poss.</p>
